ave gone untapped due to security breach fears. With VASCO’s proven anti-hack solutions, we provide convenience to your clients and the competitive edge to you. Security Solutions for Financial Institutions            Healthcare Security Solutions VASCO is a global leader in protecting the world’s most sensitive information, and offers a suite of strong, scalable and easy-to-deploy solutions tailored to help healthcare organizations protect identities, safeguard patient records, and enable compliance with regulations. We secure remote-access to patient records and monitoring devices in addition to providing the two-factor authentication required for e-prescriptions. Security Solutions for the Healthcare Industry            Government Security Solutions Governmental and public sector services can provide effective and efficient online services. To avoid identity theft or unauthorized access to confidential files, VASCO’s strong authentication solutions will replace insecure static passwords with highly secure one-time-passwords; facilitate transaction or document signing with identity-confirming electronic signatures; and encrypt data files for emails, disk and all other digital files. Security Solutions for Government Entities            e-Gaming Security Solutions The massively multiplayer online game (MMOG) industry has proven to be a popular new entertainment medium and has also become an attractive target for online fraudsters. VASCO’s two-factor authentication technology is a very simple and effective way of bridging the security gaps inherent with static passwords. With two-factor authentication, MMOG companies can regain gamers’ trust and reduce account turnover. Security Solutions for the Gaming Industry            Payments & Retail Security Solutions Online payments is a critical aspect for many industries ranging from banking to retail. VASCO’s strong authentication solutions will replace insecure static passwords with highly secure one-time-passwords; facilitate transaction or document signing with identity-confirming electronic signatures; and encrypt data files for emails, disk and all other digital files. Security Solutions for Payments & Retail Industries            Corporate News      VASCO Names Scott Clements Chief Executive Officer July 27, 2017 Read more       VASCO Reports Results for Second Quarter and First Six Months of 2017 July 27, 2017 Read more       VASCO to Announce Second Quarter 2017 Financial Results July 27, 2017 July 03, 2017 Read more     Visit our press center    Events      Aug08   ISMG Fraud and Breach Prevention Summit New York Marriott Marquis, New York City, NY, USA Read more       Aug30   17th Financial Technology & Innovation Conference Intercontinental, Miami, USA Read more       Sep04   Forum Mobile+ Pullman Vila Olimpia Hotel, Sao Paulo, Brazil Read more     All VASCO events    Blog         How to Stop the Menace of Android Rooting Malware Attacks with RASP July 17, 2017 Read more          PSD2: Simplifying the Debate on the Regulatory Technical Standards for Strong Customer Authentication July 10, 2017 Read more          PSD2 Creates Opportunities for Payment Providers but also Vulnerabilities to Mobile Users July 06, 2017 Read more         Visit our press center   All VASCO events                    SUBSCRIBE TO OUR BLOG   SUBSCRIBE                     How secure is your online business?   You have a lot to consider when it comes to choosing the right solution to secure your business. Our experts will help you find the right path.   SPEAK TO AN EXPERT                  ✖ This website uses cookies to improve user experience, functionality and performance. If you continue browsing the site, you consent to the use of cookies on this website. Note that you can change your browser/cookie settings at any time. To learn more about the use of cookies and how to adjust your settings, please read our cookie policy.     Need Help?     Chat    
        